    "$\n",
    "Normalized state:\n",
    "$\n",
    "|\\theta'\\rangle = \\frac{|+\\rangle|1\\rangle}{\\sqrt{\\frac{3}{16}}} = \\frac{4}{\\sqrt{3}} |+\\rangle|1\\rangle.\n",
